items_descriptions = {1: 'B.F. Sword - Gain Attack Damage.', 2: 'Recurve Bow - Gain Attack Speed.', 3: 'Needlessly Large Rod - Gain Spell Power.', 4: 'Tear of the Goddess - Gain Mana.', 5: 'Chain Vest - Gain Armor.', 6: 'Negatron Cloak - Gain Magic Resist.', 7: "Giant's Belt - Gain Health.", 8: 'Spatula - It must do something...', 9: 'Sparring Gloves - Gain Critical Strike Chance and Dodge Chance.', 11: 'Deathblade - Contributing to a kill grants the holder addtional Attack Damage for the rest of combat.', 12: "Giant Slayer - The holder's spells and basic attacks do bonus damage. If the target has more health, the bonus damage increases.", 13: "Hextech Gunblade - The holder's spells heal them for a percentage of the damage dealt. Excess healing fuels a shield that protects the holder.", 14: "Spear of Shojin - The holder's basic attacks restore Mana on-hit.", 15: "Guardian Angel - Prevents the wearer's first death, reviving them after a short delay and sheding all negative effects.", 16: 'Bloodthirster - Basic attacks heal the holder for a percentage of the damage dealt.', 17: "Zeke's Herald - When combat begins, the wearer and nearby allies in the same row gain Attack Speed for the rest of combat.", 18: 'Sword of the Divine - The holder gains the Divine trait.', 19: 'Infinity Edge - Grants Critical Strike Chance. Each point of Critical Strike Chance above 100% becomes bonus Critical Strike Damage.', 22: "Rapid Firecannon - The holder gains Attack Range, and their Basic Attacks can't miss.", 23: "Guinsoo's Rageblade - Basic Attacks grant bonus Attack Speed for the rest of combat.", 24: 'Statikk Shiv - Every third Basic Attack from the wearer deals Magic Damage to nearby enemies, and true damage if they are shielded or crowd-controlled.', 25: "Titan's Resolve - When the wearer takes damage or inflicts a critical hit, they gain a stacking damage bonus. The damage stacks up to a limit, at which point the wearer gains Armor and Magic Resistance, and increases in size.", 26: "Runaan's Hurricane - Basic Attacks fire a bolt at another nearby enemy, dealing a percentage of the wearer's Attack Damage and applying on-hit effects. These bolts can critical strike.", 27: "Zz'Rot Portal - When the wearer dies, a Construct arises to continue the fight.", 28: "Duelist's Zeal - The holder gains the Duelist trait.", 29: "Last Whisper - When the wearer inflicts a critical hit, the target's Armor is reduced for a number of seconds.", 33: "Rabadon's Deathcap - The holder gains additional Spell Power.", 34: "Luden's Echo - When the holder casts their spell, the first target dealt magic damage and to nearby enemies are dealt additional magic damage.", 35: 'Locket of the Iron Solari - When combat begins, the wearer and nearby allies in the same row gain a shield that blocks damage for several seconds.', 36: 'Ionic Spark - Nearby enemies have their Magic Resist reduced. When they cast a spell, they are zapped taking magic damage equal to a percentage of their max Mana.', 37: "Morellonomicon - When the holder deals damage with their spell, they burn the target, dealing a percentage of the target's maximum Health as true damage over several seconds, and reducing healing by a percentage for the duration of the burn.", 38: 'Aspect of Dusk - The holder gains the Dusk trait.', 39: "Jeweled Gauntlet - The holder's spells can cause critical hits, and the holder gains bonus Critical Strike Damage.", 44: 'Blue Buff - After casting their spell, the wearer gains Mana.', 45: 'Frozen Heart - Reduces the Attack Speed of nearby enemies. Each Frozen Heart a champion carries beyond the first increases the radius of this effect.', 46: 'Chalice of Power - When combat begins, the wearer and all nearby allies in the same row gain Spell Power for the rest of combat.', 47: 'Redemption - When the wearer dies, allies are healed.', 48: "Mage's Hat - The holder gains the Mage trait.", 49: "Hand Of Justice - At the beginning of each planning phase, the wearer's basic attacks and spells deal additional damage or heal for a percentage of damage dealt.", 55: 'Bramble Vest - Negates bonus damage from incoming critical hits. On being hit by a Basic Attack, deal magic damage to all nearby enemies.', 56: 'Gargoyle Stoneplate - The holder gains Armor and Magic Resist for each enemy targeting them.', 57: 'Sunfire Cape - At start of combat, and every couple seconds thereafter, a random nearby enemyis burned for a percentage of their maximum health. Any healing they receive is reduced.', 58: "Vanguard's Cuirass - The holder gains the Vanguard trait.", 59: "Shroud of Stillness - When combat begins, shoots a beam straight ahead that delays affected enemies' first spellcast, increasing their max Mana until they cast.", 66: "Dragon's Claw - Reduces incoming magic damage.", 67: 'Zephyr - When combat begins, the wearer summons a whirlwind on the opposite side of the arena that removes the closest enemy from combat for several seconds.', 68: 'Elderwood Sprout - The holder gains the Elderwood trait.', 69: 'Quicksilver - The wearer is immune to crowd control for the first several seconds of combat.', 77: "Warmog's Armor - Grants bonus Health.", 78: "Warlord's Banner - The wearer gains the Warlord trait.", 79: "Trap Claw - Blocks the first enemy spell that hits the wearer, and stuns the spell's caster for several seconds.", 88: 'Force of Nature - ', 89: "Youmuu's Ghostblade - The wearer gains the Assassin trait.", 99: "Thief's Gloves - At the beginning of each planning phase, the wearer equips 2 temporary items. Temporary items increase in power based on your player level."}
